rComments: This is a super cool class. She is very friendly and available for students. She knows well her topic and searches for additional information when asked. English is not her mother tongue, but it is not a problem and she manages to make the class interesting. I learned a lot in this class.

I'm sure she is very knowledgeable on the topic but she is very limited at expressing herself in english. Having her teach in french would definitely be a lot more beneficial to students in her class. English definitely not her strong point for stimulating her students.
